  scDesc: 'Attacks in a fixed vertical line across the nearest enemy, dealing 3 HP
    to all enemies caught.

    (*) Elemental Overload: Adds an additional horizontal
    line across said enemy.'
  scCommentary: Never the type to sleep in, hence I'm a big fan of dawn; nothing
    better than seeing this giant glowing fireball poke its head out after a restless
    night in the Outer Ring. Speaking of which, you'd better start giving me more
    daytime missions.
